失望。不过，对于一套很有价值的耳机来说，这些抱怨相对较小。</p><p>在 Twitter 上<em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a><em>并</em><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-best-budget-earbuds-around-are-on-sale-for-49-123026762.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-best-budget-earbuds-around-are-on-sale-for-49-123026762.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9fc8d7e2-20a6-4fbd-918d-717bd417666f </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Kris Holt]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 21 Jun 2024 12:30:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1718970880</ingested><modified> 2024-06-21T11:54:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F74121370-2fc1-11ef-baff-157756304416&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=0c2409d5a03036ac0cd7eeb1e570a50feec53be5" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri